Private Sub Display_Load() On Error Resume Next
Dim NomeTelaAtual As String NomeTelaAtual = DisplayClient.LoadedDisplays.Item("GER_RODAPE").FindElement("txtNomeTela").Caption
If ThisDisplay.Name <> NomeTelaAtual Then On Error Resume Next DisplayClient.UnloadDisplay NomeTelaAtual End If
DisplayClient.LoadedDisplays.Item("GER_RODAPE").FindElement("txtNomeTela").Caption = ThisDisplay.Name DisplayClient.LoadedDisplays.Item("GER_RODAPE").FindElement("txtNomeTela1").Caption = "TELA GERAL" End Sub
